# cursor rules for this sandbox repository

## core principles
- focus exclusively on core functionality for each feature request
- avoid feature creep and unnecessary complexity. this a sandbox
- prioritize essential user workflows 

## code style
- keep code clean and consistent
- use vanilla html css
- use async/await over promise chains
- do not generate or modify readme files

## ui/ux
- keep interface minimal and developer-friendly
- avoid unnecessary animations or complex layouts
- prefer text-first interactions with simple visual helpers

## architecture
- keep frontend (react) and backend (electron main process) separate
- isolate model integration logic in a service layer
- use small, composable components 
